	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit ad vos <persName ref="p8093" cert="high">Hercules a Salicibus</persName>, quem ut tibi commendem, non est opus, cum iam antea commendatus sit et ex virtutibus suis notus.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proficiscitur hodie in <placeName type="auto_name">Genins</placeName> ad <persName type="auto_name">Carlinum</persName>, mox inde ad vos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ardua molitur; sed non nisi ardua vincunt.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hunc tu ut consilio et re iuves, maximopere te rogo sicque mihi perusadeo te earum rerum, quas ex te scire cupit, nihil plane illum celaturum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Communis causa agitur omnium.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Er wirt by üch erkundigen, was die Stett thun werdend und ob Zürych, so man etwas ze handen nemme, ein trüw uffsechen uff unsere land haben wurde.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ir wüssend ouch, das man das korn durch und über der <persName type="auto_name">Schwytzer</persName> erdtrich von Zürych nacher fertigen muͦß.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Stunde daruff, sy verhübind dasselb.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Item so ist das gröst, wo man den baß haben möge und wie.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Daa achten ich, das der herr von <placeName type="auto_name">Sax</placeName> guͦtt zuͦ disen rädten wäre.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caetera omnia audies ex <persName type="auto_name">Hercule</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ob gott wil, gebend die üweren den baß; ob gott wil, thuͦnd sy ein oug zuͦ und lassend ouch ettliche louffen.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernenses</placeName>?</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt, sy habind inen die Ort den paß abtrutzen laßen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod scripseram <persName type="auto_name">Carlinum</persName> missurum suo nomine, de eo scias nos consilium mutasse; sufficit <persName ref="p18507" cert="high">Hercules</persName>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dum haec scribo, accipimus literas a d. <persName type="auto_name">P[aulo]</persName> <persName type="auto_name">Vergerio Thübinga</persName> scriptas, quibus se incolumem rediisse significat.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cupit, ut scribamus (sed frustra); se enim sperare, quod possit a principe reditum ad <persName type="auto_name">Rhaetos</persName> impetrare.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed <persName type="auto_name">Vergerium</persName> mittamus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ut causam hanc iuves, te iterum iterumque rogo.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, reverende in Christo pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiae</placeName> 26. iunii anno 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non est, quod mandem, operam detis, <persName ref="p18507" cert="high">Hercules</persName> a magistratu magnifice pro merito tractetur.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scitis ipsi pro vestra prudentia et humanitate, quomodo tales viri tractandi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui observans, quem nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Velim, si fieri posset et princeps de <placeName type="auto_name">Conde</placeName> scriberet, aliquis illorum etiam singulariter ad <persName type="auto_name">Carlinum</persName> scriberet, ne videretur negligi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
